n THIS little notebook from Amstrad is described as the world's
easiest-to-operate computer, and one which everyone can learn to use in fewer
than five minutes. Amstrad say they'll refund the money if it's an idle boast.
The Notebook NC200 is a full-function word processor with spellchecker,
calendar and diary, spreadsheet facility and some games included. It's also got
