n Best concert - This was The Clash Complete Control tour in 1978 when I was
still a plastic punk. It was held at The Apollo and was a real eye-opener.
There was no gobbing or posturing or posing. They were dead gallus, totally
cool and brilliant lyrics. After that I changed from a plastic to a real punk.
n Worst concert - This was when The Bluebells got invited over by the Maltese
